The paper deals with graph theory and algorithms related to independent sets and chromatic number. Specifically, it focuses on the induced odd cycle packing number of graphs and its relationship to independent sets and chromatic number. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
